Package org.stringmatching.hybrid.ahocorasick_wumanber

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AC_WM_Matcher
    This is an implementation of the hybrid multiple pattern matching from http://www.just.edu.jo/~munzer/MyPubs/Hybrid.pdf The premise is to exploit the fact that WM is inefficient for short strings and AC performance degrades for longer strings.
    AC_WM_Pattern
    Build the the Pattern Model for the hybrid method.
    Token
    Represent the information for one token
